-- Spaniards May Use Pensions to Cut Loan Arrears, Expansion Says
-- B y   E s t e b a n   D u a r t e
-- 2012-04-28T12:33:38Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-28/spaniards-may-use-pensions-to-cut-loan-arrears-expansion-says.html
Spain  may allow homeowners in
arrears to redeem pension funds ahead of the legal minimum age
to avoid their property being repossessed,  Expansion  said,
citing a draft version of a rule being considered by the
government.  The law may come into force before the end of the year, the
newspaper said.  To contact the reporters on this story:
Esteban Duarte in Madrid at 
